.TH devin-mcp-login 1  "login " 
.SH NAME
devin\-mcp\-login \- Authenticate with an MCP server via OAuth
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin mcp login\fR [\fB\-\-scopes\fR] [\fB\-\-oauth\-client\-id\fR] [\fB\-\-oauth\-client\-secret\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fINAME\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Authenticate with an MCP server via OAuth
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-scopes\fR \fI<SCOPE,SCOPE>\fR
OAuth scopes to request (comma\-separated)
.TP
\fB\-\-oauth\-client\-id\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Pre\-registered OAuth client ID for servers that don\*(Aqt support dynamic client registration (e.g. GitHub)
.TP
\fB\-\-oauth\-client\-secret\fR \fI<SECRET>\fR
OAuth client secret (for confidential clients)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fINAME\fR>
Server name to authenticate with
